            "body": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/10504 probably related.\r\n\r\nWould be great if a client could subscribe to receive additional highlight group in `hl_group_set`. That alone might be a bit different from what @folke is asking for, unless the `hl_*` events were extracted to their own `ext_` group.\r\n\r\nI'm currently doing stuff like this to get additional colors: https://github.com/vhakulinen/gnvim/blob/b8cc1bc78a94948041d37ddaf3d0ef05b45df40b/runtime/lua/gnvim/init.lua#L56-L79\r\n\r\nDownside of that is it doesn't handle updates to any colors automatically.",
